n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（表示 n 个个体都在个体域 D 上取值） 上取值于{0,1}上的 n 元函数，称为 \u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003en 元命题函数\u003c/font\u003e或 \u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003en 元谓词 (Propositional Function)\u003c/font\u003e，记为 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"P(x_1, x_2, …, x_n)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。此时，个体变量 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"x_1, x_2, …, x_n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的定义域都为 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"D"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"P(x_1, x_2, …, x_n)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的值域为{0, 1｝"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-687uho4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-687uho4","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"定义 5.1.4"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-af3byx3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-af3byx3","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"称 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"(\\large \\forall x)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 为\u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003e全称量词（Universal Quantifier）\u003c/font\u003e ， "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"(\\large \\exists x)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 为\u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003e存在量词（ Existential Quantifier）\u003c/font\u003e，其中的 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"x"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 称为\u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003e作用变量（Function Variable）\u003c/font\u003e。一般将其量词加在其谓词之前，记为 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"(\\large \\forall x)F(x)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"(\\large \\exists x)F(x)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。此时，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"F(x)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 称为全称量词和存在量词的\u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003e辖域 (Scope)\u003c/font\u003e。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-jwn9mkk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-jwn9mkk","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"定义 5.1.5"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-3d4beym","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-3d4beym","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"统一个体域为\u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003e全总个体域\u003c/font\u003e，而对每一个句子中个体变量的变化范围用一元\u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003e特性谓词\u003c/font\u003e刻划之。这种特性谓词在加入到命题函数中时必定遵循如下原则："}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-3i8n32a","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":41,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-3i8n32a","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082132-t4gqnd1","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":41,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-t4gqnd1","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082132-1xc8kje","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-1xc8kje","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于全称量词 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"(\\forall x)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，刻划其对应个体域的特性谓词作为蕴涵式之前件加入。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-gl2ko2n","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":41,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-gl2ko2n","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082132-razg4iy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-razg4iy"