"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-by96a72","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082132-2m80gx4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-2m80gx4","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"公式 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"G"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 称为\u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003e可满足公式\u003c/font\u003e， 如果至少有一种解释 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"I"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 使得 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"G"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 取值为“真”。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-rnll9cm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-rnll9cm","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.3.6 谓词公式的可判定性"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-2klanir","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":41,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-2klanir","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082132-80pas5t","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":41,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-80pas5t","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082132-ozihn1b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-ozihn1b","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"谓词逻辑是不可判定的；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-nmfhlvf","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":41,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-nmfhlvf","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082132-nfcp81d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-nfcp81d","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"只含有一元谓词变项的公式是可判定的；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-rktdqdz","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":41,"Padding":3,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-rktdqdz","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082132-4do4s7t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-4do4s7t","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"个体域有穷时的谓词公式是可判定的。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-akh20a6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-akh20a6","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.3.7 谓词合式公式的基本等价关系"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-4fjaju9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-4fjaju9","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"公式 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"G"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"H"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 称为\u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003e等价的 (Equivalent)\u003c/font\u003e， 记为 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G = H"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，如果公式 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G \\leftrightarrow H"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是有效公式。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-0utitep","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-0utitep","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"设 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G(P_1, P_2,…, P_n)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是命题演算中的命题公式，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"P_1, P_2, …, P_n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"G"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 中的命题变元，当用任意的谓词公式 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G_i(1\\leq i\\leq n)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 分别代入 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"P_i"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 后，得到的新谓词公式 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G(G_1, G_2,…, G_n)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 称为原公式的\u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003e代入实例\u003c/font\u003e。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-ahrou00","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-ahrou00","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.4 谓词的标准型 - 范式"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-dg3x028","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-dg3x028","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在命题逻辑里，每一公式都有与之等值的范式， 范式是一种\u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003e统一的表达形式\u003c/font\u003e，当研究一个公式的特点 (如永真、永假) 时，范式起着重要作用。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-y6k8t2v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-y6k8t2v","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对谓词逻辑的公式来说，也有范式，其中前束范式与原公式是等值的，而其它范式与原公式只有较弱的关系。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-5cmsxq9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-5cmsxq9","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.4.1 前束范式"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-7cnwjo0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-7cnwjo0","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"称公式 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"G"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是一个前束范式，如果 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"G"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 中的一切量词都位于该公式的最前端 (不含否定词) 且这些量词的辖域都延伸到公式的末端。其标准形式如下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-i7kivkf","Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-i7kivkf","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"\\huge\n(Q_1x_1)(Q_2x_2)...(Q_nx_n)M(x_1,x_2,...,x_n)"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-6ttc9z3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-6ttc9z3","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其中 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"Q_i(i=1,2,…,n)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 为量词 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\forall"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 或 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\exists"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"M"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 称作公式 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"G"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的母式 (基式)，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"M"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 中不再有量词"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-k8ln54w","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-k8ln54w","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e "},{"ID":"20260305082132-9o05yfj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-9o05yfj","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"定理"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-xmyfoq4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-xmyfoq4","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"谓词逻辑中的任一公式都可化为与之等价的前束范式，但其前束范式并不唯一。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-034skz6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-034skz6","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.4.2 Skolem 标准型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-f13nty8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-f13nty8","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"设公式 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"G"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是一个前束范式，如消去 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"G"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 中所有的存在量词和全称量词，所得到的公式称为 \u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003eSkolem 标准型\u003c/font\u003e。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-fe3b7gk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-fe3b7gk","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"任意一个公式 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"G"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 都有相应的 Skolem 标准形存在，但\u003cfont color=\"#245bdb\"\u003e此 Skolem 标准形不一定与原公式等值\u003c/font\u003e。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-ttrnszv","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-ttrnszv","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Skolem 标准型的转换步骤"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-0tdfj1j","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-0tdfj1j","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082132-1thz78t","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-1thz78t","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082132-fm7ypm2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-fm7ypm2","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"消去蕴含号 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"(\\to)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 用等价变形消除所有的蕴含符号："}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-qxpph8h","Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-qxpph8h","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"\\huge\nA\\to B =\\lnot A\\lor B"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockCloseMarker"}]}