,"Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-mrhbn7f","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"\\huge\n\\begin{matrix}\n(\\Gamma \\land P)\\Rightarrow S 等价于\\Gamma \\Rightarrow (P\\to S)\\\\ \n(Q \\land P) \\to S = Q \\to (P\\to S)\n\\end{matrix}"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-cbuipns","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-cbuipns","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6.1.2.4 间接证明法（反证法）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-e282oak","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-e282oak","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"前面使用过的一些证明方法都是正向推理。但在数学领域中，经常会遇到一些问题，当采用正向推理时很难从前提为真推出结论为真。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-uhw3bwx","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-uhw3bwx","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20260305082132-mx9vp1h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-mx9vp1h","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"P\\Rightarrow Q"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 等价于 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\lnot Q\\Rightarrow \\lnot P"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，因此，为了间接地证明 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"P\\Rightarrow Q"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，可以假设 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"Q"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 为假 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"(\\lnot Q)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，然后证明 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"P"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 为假 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"(\\lnot P)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-c6r3psc","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-c6r3psc","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"定义"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-qsu9dn1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-qsu9dn1","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"假设 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G_1,G_2,…,G_n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是一组命题公式，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"P_1,P_2,…,P_n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是出现在其中的一切命题变元 ， 若有解释 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"I"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 使 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G_1\\land G_2\\land …\\land G_n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 取值为“真”，则称公式 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G_1,G_2,…,G_n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是一致的，或者说是相容的。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-ak6mb3j","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-ak6mb3j","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"定理"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-ch18n6m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-ch18n6m","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"设命题公式集合 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\{G_1,G_2,…,G_n\\}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是一致的， 于是从前提集合 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"{G_1,G_2,…,G_n}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 出发可以逻辑地推出公式 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"H"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的充要条件是从前提集合 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"{G_1, G_2,…,G_n,\\lnot H}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 出发，可以逻辑地推出一个矛盾（永假）式来。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-qj4bjnx","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-qj4bjnx","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6.2 谓词逻辑的推理理论"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-2l5sdwn","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-2l5sdwn","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6.2.1 谓词演算的演绎与推理"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-w2s7j9f","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-w2s7j9f","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"定义"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-c9g41mc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-c9g41mc","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"设 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G_1, G_2, …,G_n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"H"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是公式，称 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"H"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G_1, G_2, …,G_n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的逻辑结果 （"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G_1, G_2, …,G_n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 共同蕴涵 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"H"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ），当且仅当 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"H"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G_1\\land G_2\\land…\\land G_n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的\u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003e逻辑结果 (logic conclusion)\u003c/font\u003e。记为 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G_1, G_2, …,G_n\\Rightarrow H"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，此时称 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G_1, G_2, …,G_n\\Rightarrow H"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 为\u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003e有效的 (efficacious)\u003c/font\u003e，否则称为 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"无效的（inefficacious）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G_1, G_2, …,G_n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 称为一组\u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003e前提 (Premise)\u003c/font\u003e,有时用集合 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\Gamma"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 来表示，记 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\Gamma = \\{G_1, G_2, …,G_n\\}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"H"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 称为\u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003e结论 (conclusion)\u003c/font\u003e。又称 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"H"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是前提集合的逻辑结果。记为 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\Gamma \\Rightarrow H"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-3u378qg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-3u378qg","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"定理"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-7kco3d1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-7kco3d1","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"公式 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"H"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是前提集合 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\Gamma = \\{G_1, G_2, …,G_n\\}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的逻辑结果当且仅当 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G_1\\land G_2\\land…\\land G_n\\to H"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 为\u003cfont color=\"#ff0000\"\u003e有效公式\u003c/font\u003e。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-ujunqg9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-ujunqg9","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6.2.2 推理规律"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-yooll01","Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-yooll01","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"\\huge\n\\begin{align}\n1)\\ \u0026I_{16}:(\\forall x)G(x)\\Rightarrow (\\exists x)G(x)\\\\\n\\\\\n2)\\ \u0026I_{17}:(\\forall x)G(x)\\lor(\\forall x)H(x)\\Rightarrow (\\forall x)(G(x)\\lor H(x))\\\\\n\u0026I_{17}中右式弱于左式 ，反向不成立\\\\\n\\\\\n\u0026E:(\\forall x)G(x)\\lor(\\forall x)H(x)\\Rightarrow (\\forall x)(\\forall y)(G(x)\\lor H(y))\\\\\n\u0026这个式子右式与左式等价，反向成立\\\\\n\\\\\n\u0026I_{18}:(\\exists x)(G(x)\\land H(x))\\Rightarrow (\\exists x)G(x)\\land(\\exists x)H(x)\\\\\n\\\\\n3)\\ \u0026I_{19}:(\\forall x)(G(x)\\to H(x))\\Rightarrow (\\exists x)G(x)\\to(\\exists x)H(x)\\\\\n\u0026I_{20}:(\\forall x)(G(x)\\to H(x))\\Rightarrow (\\forall x)G(x)\\to(\\forall x)H(x)\\\\\n\\\\\n4)\\ \u0026I_{21}:(\\exists x)(\\forall y)G(x,y)\\Rightarrow (\\forall y)(\\exists x)G(x,y)\\\\\n\u0026I_{22}:(\\forall x)(\\forall y)G(x,y)\\Rightarrow (\\exists y)(\\forall x)G(x,y)\\\\\n\u0026I_{23}:(\\forall y)(\\forall x)G(x,y)\\Rightarrow (\\exists x)(\\forall y)G(x,y)\\\\\n\u0026I_{24}:(\\exists y)(\\forall x)G(x,y)\\Rightarrow (\\forall x)(\\exists y)G(x,y)\\\\\n\u0026I_{25}:(\\forall x)(\\exists y)G(x,y)\\Rightarrow (\\exists y)(\\exists x)G(x,y)\\\\\n\u0026I_{26}:(\\forall y)(\\exists x)G(x,y)\\Rightarrow (\\exists x)(\\exists y)G(x,y)\\\\\n\\end{align}"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-xnt278i","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-xnt278i","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"量词关系图"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-watl51j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-watl51j","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"![[量词关系图.png]]"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-9n0ycaf","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-9n0ycaf","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6.2.3 推理规则"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-guocjnh","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-guocjnh","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. US（全称特指规则，Universal SPecify）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-w4mn4tp","Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-w4mn4tp","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"\\huge\n(\\forall x)G(x) \\Rightarrow G(y)"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-zjbfpxh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-zjbfpxh","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其中 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"G(x)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 对 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"y"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是自由的"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-bvh1qkp","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-bvh1qkp","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e "},{"ID":"20260305082132-rs5gnky","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":