","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-ecbw6um","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6.4 按定义证明方法 （CP 规则证明）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-id9sclh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-id9sclh","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在离散数学中，我们大量的定义描述都是用蕴涵型“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"P\\to Q"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”的方式来描述的。如集合中子集的包含关系的定义描述为："}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-7ddt4fp","Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-7ddt4fp","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"\\huge\nA \\subseteq B \\Leftrightarrow (\\forall a)(a\\in A\\to a\\in B)"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockCloseMarker"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-0qz6m2q","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-0qz6m2q","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6.4.1 按定义证明方法原理"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-t60qhff","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-t60qhff","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"设有一组前提 (或叫做已知条件) 为 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\Gamma =\\{G_1,G_2, …,G_n\\}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，证明问题 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"H = P\\to Q"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，则利用 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"CP"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 规则的证明方式，将证明问题 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"H"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 中的前提 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"P"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 作为附加前提，加入到前提集合当中，构成一组新前提 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\Gamma' =\\{G_1,G_2, …,G_n,P\\}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，此时，证明这组新前提 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\Gamma'\\Rightarrow Q"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，即有"}]},{"ID":"20260305082132-4mleueu","Type":"NodeMathBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082132-4mleueu","updated":"20260305082132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeMathBlockOpenMarker"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockContent","Data":"\\huge\n\\Gamma \\Rightarrow H  \\overset{CP}{\\Leftrightarrow} \\Gamma' \\Rightarrow Q"},{"Type":"NodeMathBlockCloseMarker"}]}]}